title: How to Play Guitar: A Beginners Guide to Learning Guitar
description:
http://ititli.com/images/8jTlkVuOP.jpg

How to Play Guitar is for the beginner guitar player, this 51 page mini-ebook contains 64 exercises of TABS as well as chord charts and fretboard diagrams showing you the basics of playing guitar.

How to Play Guitar: A Beginners Guide to Learning Guitar by Matthew Christey
English | 12 Sept. 2016 | ASIN: B01LYGWBHL | 51 Pages | True PDF | 3.99 MB
